<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/Gantt" AddedVersion="Added in v2.0">
    Blazorise Gantt component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Build timeline-driven planning experiences with a synchronized tree and timeline view.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    The <Code>Gantt</Code> component is designed for project planning use cases where tasks have hierarchy, dates, duration, and progress. It supports declarative columns, built-in editing, keyboard and mouse interactions, and template-based customization.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    To use the <Code>Gantt</Code> component, install the <Code>Blazorise.Gantt</Code> package first.
</DocsPageParagraph>

