</DocsPageSection>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="External Editing">
        By setting the <Code>UseInternalEditing=false</Code> Gantt raises command callbacks with the relevant item and context, but leaves the editing UI and persistence flow to your implementation. This is ideal for keeping Gantt as a pure view component while owning the user experience and data flow of your app.
